      "properties": {
        "text": "🎯 节点分组说明\n\n所有 Moyin Creator 节点按功能分组：\n\n👤 Character (角色)\n  - 🪄 Create Character\n  - ✨ Character to Prompt\n\n🎬 Scene (场景)\n  - 🎬 Create Scene\n  - 📚 Combine Scenes\n\n✨ Prompt (提示词)\n  - 🖼️ Build Image Prompt\n  - 🎥 Build Video Prompt\n  - 🚫 Build Negative Prompt\n  - 🎨 Scene to Image Prompt\n\n📖 Screenplay (剧本)\n  - 📖 Create Screenplay"
      }
    },
